## Zeek + Splunk Beaconing Query

```splunk
index=network sourcetype=zeek_conn
| where NOT cidrmatch("10.0.0.0/8",id.resp_h)
  AND NOT cidrmatch("192.168.0.0/16",id.resp_h)
  AND NOT cidrmatch("172.16.0.0/12",id.resp_h)
| bucket _time span=5m
| stats count by id.orig_h, id.resp_h, 
        id.resp_p, _time
| stats stdev(count) as beacon_stdev
        avg(count) as beacon_avg
        min(count) as beacon_min
        max(count) as beacon_max
        count as intervals
  by id.orig_h, id.resp_h, id.resp_p
| where intervals > 12 AND beacon_stdev < 1.5
| eval regularity_score = 
    round((1 - beacon_stdev/(beacon_avg+0.001))*100,1)
| where regularity_score > 80
| sort - regularity_score
```

